solution:
The matrix
\[\begin{pmatrix} \cos 170^\circ & -\sin 170^\circ \\ \sin 170^\circ & \cos 170^\circ \end{pmatrix}\]corresponds to rotating the origin by an angle of $170^\circ$ counter-clockwise.

[asy]
unitsize(2 cm);

